Computers, Kinds of Computers in respect of size and function,

Computer - Computer recives data through a input unit processes the data into a meaningful information and sends the information to the output device.
Computer is also known as IPM - Information Processing Machine

Computer that was made in the beginning was huge, slow and had kimited capabilities ; Todays modern computers are fast, accurate, versatile, automatic, diligence and have high storgae. 

Characteristics of Computer:
Speed - Computer is based on two different states of electricity and they are: on & off. The data and instructions flow in the computer through electric circuits at the speed of light i.e 3.2 x 10^8 m/s . It is the main reason why computer can process huge amount of data in less period of time. 
